Secure File Access Control System
A comprehensive enterprise-grade file security platform powered by AI, Blockchain, and Military Encryption technologies.

üåü Overview
Secure File Access Control is a sophisticated web application that provides advanced file security management with real-time threat detection, immutable audit trails, and military-grade encryption. The system offers role-based access control with separate interfaces for administrators and regular users.

‚ú® Key Features
üîê Security & Authentication
Role-based Access Control (Admin/User roles)

Secure Login System with session management

Military-grade AES-256 Encryption for file protection

Password-protected file uploads with client-side encryption

ü§ñ AI-Powered Threat Detection
Real-time ML Analysis of uploaded files

Multiple ML Models (Random Forest, SVM, Isolation Forest)

Confidence Scoring for threat assessment

Automated Risk Classification (Allow/Deny/Review)

‚õìÔ∏è Blockchain Integration
Immutable Audit Trail for all file access events

